posts.text:
University of Michigan Patient Services Senior in Ann Arbor , Michigan 
Job Summary 
The Kellogg Eye Center is an internationally respected department as part of Michigan Medicine. We provide over 175,000 patient visits per year in 10 different locations in and surrounding Ann Arbor. With 100 faculty members, 21 residents, and 10 clinical fellows we strive to provide the best eye care available anywhere in the world. Our purpose is to improve lives through curing, treating, and preventing eye disease. Our guiding principles are teamwork, caring, integrity, and innovation. Together, we use our purpose and guiding principles to align ourselves both as individuals and as an organization to achieve our vision of improving lives around the world by enhancing vision in others. We are a USNWR top 10 program and are seeking individuals who wish to enhance the strength and capability of our workforce to help us become even better at the work that we do. 
Responsibilities* 
The Senior Coordinator/Specialist will oversee the coordination and management of all surgery and billing functions in the Kellogg Eye Center Grand Blanc office. As the only non-HOPD facility in the KEC community of offices, surgery scheduling and billing functions will be primarily managed onsite. On a day-to-day basis, responsibilities include but are not limited to: 
Utilize EMR to access patient information and perform routine and higher level clerical functions 
Schedule appointments, surgery and ancillary testing within the Michigan Medicine system and at outside facilities 
Assist patients with payment questions, collect payments and arrange payment plans 
Process authorization for services and procedures 
Manage and process referral and authorization work queues for surgery and billing 
Act as KEC’s liaison with partnering surgery centers outside of the Michigan Medicine network 
Monitor compliance with local networks 
Schedule and document surgery details and communicate with interdisciplinary teams at multiple surgery center locations 
Serve as representative of the surgery schedule team on various committees and workgroups to promote standards of care and process improvement 
Participate actively in efforts to improve processes that will enhance the experience on internal and external customers, including the lean in daily work huddles and processes 
Collaborate with staff to ensure proper coordination of services and contribution to patient satisfaction 
The ideal candidate will possess excellent written and oral communication skills, a team based orientation, a high level of professionalism and diligence to identify and reduce errors and inefficiencies that contribute to decreased patient satisfaction or clinical outcomes. Additionally, the ideal candidate will be an advocate for patients and their access to the highest quality ophthalmic care regardless of perceived background or insurance status. The Surgery Coordinator/Billing Specialist must support faculty, staff, and patients within the clinic, and ultimately, the Department of Ophthalmology while fostering the fulfillment of Michigan Medicine’s tripartite mission. 
Required Qualifications* 
High school diploma or GED 
5+ years of progressively responsible experience in health care 
Knowledge of basic medical terminology 
Demonstrated ability to lead a team or project 
Experience facilitating and coordinating a patient’s continuum of care, as well as, identifying and recommending appropriate resources available. 
Exceptional interpersonal skills and ability to work well within a team setting. 
Communicates effectively. 
Demonstrates active listening, written, verbal and information technology skills . 
Desired Qualifications* 
Associates or Bachelor’s Degree 
Experience or knowledge in the field of ophthalmology 
Previous experience with MiChart (Epic) or other electronic medical record (EMR) 
Experience working within a large, complex health care setting 
Proficient in programs and applications for reporting of metric data 
Previous leadership experience 
Familiarity with University policies and KEC guiding principles that promote Caring, Teamwork, Integrity and Innovation 
Work Schedule 
Monday-Friday, dependent on clinic operation hours 
Background Screening 
Michigan Medicine conducts background screening and pre-employment drug testing on job candidates upon acceptance of a contingent job offer and may use a third party administrator to conduct background screenings. Background screenings are performed in compliance with the Fair Credit Report Act. 
Mission Statement 
Michigan Medicine improves the health of patients, populations and communities through excellence in education, patient care, community service, research and technology development, and through leadership activities in Michigan, nationally and internationally. Our mission is guided by our Strategic Principles and has three critical components; patient care, education and research that together enhance our contribution to society. 
Application Deadline 
Job openings are posted for a minimum of seven calendar days. This job may be removed from posting boards and filled anytime after the minimum posting period has ended. 
U-M EEO/AA Statement 
The University of Michigan is an equal opportunity/affirmative action employer.

posts.text:
Media Relations 서스틴베스트 "사회적 책임 기업이 주가 상승률도 우수" 3시간 전 URL 복사 본문 기타 기능 번역보기 http://blog.naver.com/sustinvest/221134708263 사회적 책임을 준수하는 기업의 주가가 코스피지수 상승률보다 높은 것으로 나타났다.
7일 사회적 책임투자 컨설팅 업체 서스틴베스트에 따르면 환경·사회·지배구조(ESG) 점수가 양호한 ‘투자가능종목군’ 상장사들의 최근 7년간 평균 주가 수익률은 30.8%로 코스피지수 상승률(27.57%)보다 3%포인트 이상 높았다.
같은 기간 주요 기업들로 구성된 코스피200의 수익률(29.93%)보다도 높은 상승률을 보였다.
(중략)
서스틴베스트는 매년 상장사의 환경경영(E), 사회책임경영(S), 지배구조(G) 현황을 평가해 최우수 등급인 AA부터 최하 E등급까지 7개로 나눠 평가하고 있다.
한편 ESG 성과가 좋은 기업은 상대적으로 자기자본이익률(ROE)도 높은 것으로 나타났다.
서스틴베스트가 최근 3년간 520여개 상장사의 ESG 점수와 ROE의 상관관계를 분석한 결과 ESG 상위 25%의 ROE가 나머지 75% 기업보다 높았다.
서스틴베스트 관계자는 “ESG 요소가 기업의 재무성과와 투자수익률에 프리미엄으로 작용한다는 것을 보여주는 것”이라고 말했다.

Imer, la minoranza se ne va 
Dimissioni in Consiglio Bettega: "Impossibile collaborare con la Giunta" Mar, 07/11/2017 - 09:29 ! minuto 52 secondi 
Da lunedì 6 novembre il Comune di Imer non ha più una minoranza. 
I componenti della lista elettorale «Per Imer» hanno depositato in mattinata presso il comune le irrevocabili dimissioni da consiglieri.Alla base della decisione una complicata convivenza con il sindaco Gianni Bellotto , tanto da portare il gruppo di maggioranza, a questa forte decisione. 
Gli ormai ex consiglieri Pio Decimo Bettega, Dino Doff Sotta, Silvano Angelani, Hanna Marianna Wittmann e Anna Tomas non verranno sostituiti.Anche i componenti della lista perdente le elezioni del 2015 che non erano entrati in consiglio si sono infatti dichiarati indisponibili ad assumere la carica di consigliere. Il Comune di Imer proseguirà così la legislatura con la sola maggioranza.«Noi della minoranza abbiamo fatto diverse interrogazioni - afferma il capogruppo Pio Decimo Bettega - che non sono state prese in considerazione, rendendo così impossibile qualsiasi dialogo. Sono state fatte tante promesse dalla maggioranza, ma i fatti non si sono visti. Il paese sta andando allo sfascio e non vogliamo più essere partecipi del degrado del paese. Speriamo che vadano avanti lo stesso anche senza di noi».Molte le critiche fatte dalla minoranza. Gli spazi verdi e i parchi non curati, la condizione delle strade, lo scarso allacciamento dei privati al teleriscaldamento, la mancanza di parcheggi che obbliga le macchine a parcheggiare a lato della strada, con pericoli per i pedoni in transito. 
«Dal 2010 sono pronti i progetti per i parcheggi interrati sotto le scuole e sotto il municipio - continua Pio Decimo - ma visto che li abbiamo proposti noi nella precedente legislatura tutto è ancora fermo».Viene contestata inoltre la manutenzione della zona in località Giare. «La maggioranza disse che la avrebbe sistemata, invece è stato aggiunto altro degrado a quello già esistente». 
Vengono poi criticati i ritardi nei lavori di sistemazione della discarica e l’errata tempistica dei lavori al cimitero, cominciati solo qualche giorno prima del giorno di Tutti i Santi. «L’archivio storico della canonica di Imer è stato trasferito a Mezzano. Con tuti i locali vuoti che ha Imer, non si poteva tenere qua? Perché lo hanno portato a Mezzano?» si chiede Pio Decimo, secondo il quale il comune sarebbe in conflitto anche con il Gruppo Attività Ricreative Imer (G.A.R.I.), avendo ignorato le sue recenti attività.

posts.title: 納豆調戲莎莎！﹖ 食尚一姐驚嘆「演藝圈好黑暗」
posts.text:
( (《食尚玩家》莎莎與納豆)
【WoWoNews】曾一起合作拍TVBS偶像劇《我們結婚吧》的莎莎、納豆，相隔十年後終於再度合作，為TVBS歡樂台《食尚玩家》在雙北尋找爆炸人氣美食小吃。由於人氣美食都要花時間排隊，莎莎覺得演藝圈中，納豆最有趣，所以找他來一起消磨排隊的無聊時光。行程間，納豆不愧為「美食界小巨人」，對排隊美食熟門熟路，他們倆去排了吳宗憲也很愛的梅干控肉烤包子、以及好吃到日本人都遠道而來，只能站在路邊吃的早餐，納豆推薦想認識日本妹的觀眾快來此！還有從《食尚玩家》開播時製作單位就想拍攝，但老闆一直拒絕，終於在節目開播十年，才答應採訪的麻辣火鍋店。吃飽喝足後，納豆帶莎莎去一家溫馨小店喝茶休息，貼心的舉動讓莎莎覺得男生就要像納豆這樣，溫馨又會安排行程，她忍不住虧納豆︰「難怪你妹都停不了！」目前單身的納豆苦笑回說「最近很乾涸！」

莎莎還帶來和納豆拍戲時的照片，短髮青春的納豆，讓他感嘆歲月催人老。納豆回憶以前從不覺得莎莎是美女，只覺得她是個很親切的人，但現在「女大十八變」，是位大美女。對於納豆描述莎莎以往不美之說，莎莎立刻反駁︰「你記得你以前有調戲過我嗎！」驚悚言語讓納豆尖叫駁斥！回憶這段過往，莎莎說十年前有次她蹲在路邊等拍戲，納豆走過去，作勢要親她，嘴唇啾起來啵的一下就走了，突然的舉動讓莎莎只想著︰「納哥怎麼這樣﹖別過來！」納豆反問︰「我有碰到妳嗎﹖」莎莎表示雖然沒有碰到，只是空氣親，但這是她人生第一次被調戲，當時還是演藝新人，心中就覺得︰「演藝圈好黑暗！」面對莎莎的指控，納豆無奈的打趣說這是「潛規則」。

posts.text:
Para las que no sepan, la WNBA es lo mismo que la NBA, pero de mujeres. Como la WTA en el tenis. Y como la WTA, la WNBA no posee la misma atención y fanaticada que sus contrapartes masculinas. A pesar de lo que diga Candice Wiggins, esto no tiene nada que ver con que, en el caso de la WNBA, (según ella) « el 98% de las jugadoras son lesbianas »*. Sino porque vivimos en una sociedad machista. No importa lo bien que lo hagan las chicas, los chicos siempre recibirán mejor atención.
Sino miren el caso de la selección femenina de fútbol de los Estados Unidos, que han sido campeonas del mundo en tres ocasiones y las Olimpiadas cuatro veces. Son las número uno del mundo y lo más bajo que han llegado en el ranking FIFA es la segunda posición.
Y aun así, los hombres, que no han hecho nada bueno en la historia del fútbol, ganan más, tienen más apoyo económico y moral .
Elena y Amanda Una publicación compartida de Amanda Clifton (@mandaclif) el 16 de Feb de 2017 a la(s) 5:59 PST 
Pero lo importante aquí es Elena Donne , que es una de las jugadoras estrellas del baloncesto femenino estadounidense y mundial. Tiene 28 años, mide 1,96 metros y actualmente juega con las Washington Mystics, además de la selección nacional.
MVP del 2015, novata del año en 2013 y campeona olímpica en 2016 .
Una publicación compartida de Amanda Clifton (@mandaclif) el 20 de Ago de 2016 a la(s) 2:13 PDT 
Amanda es actualmente, además de la esposa de Elena, la directora de la Academia De11e Donne (desde 2014). Antes trabajó para una compañía de seguros. Además solía jugar baloncesto en la universidad. Así se conocieron, entrenando juntas en Delaware.
Y lo hacen todo juntas, porque además ambas crean mesas que luego venden en Etsy .
Una publicación compartida de Amanda Clifton (@mandaclif) el 2 de Nov de 2016 a la(s) 4:06 PDT

Canterbury skipper gets All Blacks call-up Tue, 07 Nov 2017 09:14 
SQUAD UPDATE: Highlanders and Canterbury loose forward Luke Whitelock has been called into the All Blacks squad as cover for Jerome Kaino. 
The 26-year-old Whitelock played for the Barbarians against the All Blacks at Twickenham last week and has now joined the team in Paris ahead of this weekend's test against France. 
He has one All Blacks test cap to his name after coming on as a substitute in a 54-6 win over Japan in Tokyo 2013. 
Kaino injured his posterior cruciate ligament in the All Blacks 31-22 win over the Baabaas and remains in doubt for the rest of the tour. 
Whitelock's call-up is not a good sign for the 81-test veteran Kaino, who wants to re-establish his place in the squad. 
Whitelock's presence takes the squad to 43 players but he is unlikely to feature against France.

10週年、全球惟一亞洲場的「ARCADIA電子音樂節」最強場次，就要在11月11日和12日光棍節周末登陸、正式「入侵」台北大佳河濱公園！從2007年開始的「ARCADIA電子音樂節」，不僅連開2天並邀來8組世界級百大冠軍DJ；還有3組台灣DJ組合藝人：XN藍洞樂團、DJ Noodles麵麵與麻吉弟弟Machi DiDi。

麻吉弟弟Machi DiDi10月27日才剛推出數位EP「大逆有道」；而XN藍洞樂團的仕翔也預告：「XN藍洞樂團在11月11日的ARCADIA電子音樂節上，也確定發表1首由傑妮擔任主唱的新創作，而這首歌也會是以中文演唱的！」還有EDM及勸世音樂傳奇先鋒的Paul van Dyk，也透過影片向台灣樂迷們預告：「我將於11月11日於ARCADIA台灣站演出，我會播放很多新專輯『魔神啟航』（From Then On)裡的新歌！」 

Paul van Dyk在2016演出時不慎跌落舞台，差點失去性命的他在復健期間思考沉澱，發展成這張新專輯「魔神啟航」（From Then On)，回歸最原始直接的重拍衝擊；也重新開發音樂的視野。巧合的是，這張實體專輯在台灣推出的時間也是10月27日！而也因爲2天總共有11組DJ連番登台轟炸，主辦單位COSMOS LIVE!也宣布：2天的入場時間都將提前至13:30，活動也將提前至14:00開始！ 

而「ARCADIA電子音樂節」除了有去年就已經帶來的，視聽同步震撼的大蜘蛛舞台噴火秀外；今年更加碼真人雷電對打秀，準備讓現場樂迷們近距離感受360度的全方位震撼與魅力。

posts.text: / 5 SHOCKING things that decrease your sperm count 5 SHOCKING things that decrease your sperm count By Bhavyajyoti Chilukoti   1:51 pm Tags: Sperm count Did you ever think that watching TV and leading a sedentary lifestyle can put you at risk of low sperm count? Here are few such things that are known to decrease sperm count based on research studies. Hot water baths: It was proved that 30 minutes of hot water bath lowers sperm count. A recent study [1] revealed that men who cut down the exposure to hot baths showed a 491% increase in the sperm count. A study [2] showed that men who watched 20 hours of T.V or more a week actually had 50% lesser sperm count than those who do not watch T.V at all. Get up and talk a walk than watch TV! Arvind Vaid, a city-based IVF expert, said that breathing too much of pollution leads to a higher concentration of free radicals in the blood, that causes a lower sperm quality even in fertile men. If you place a laptop on the lap, not only the heat from it warm men’s scrotums, the electromagnetic fields generated by laptop’s internal electronic circuits and Wi-Fi may decrease sperm quality [3]. Stop placing your laptops on your lap. Western diet: Yes, if you like bingeing on western foods like pizza and canned foods, then it's high time to avoid it. posts.title: 28.《在回家的路上》(王上13:11-34)
posts.text:
這事以後，耶羅波安仍不離開他的惡道，將凡民立為邱壇的祭司；凡願意的，他都分別為聖，立為邱壇的祭司。 ( 王上 13:33) 
猶大 來 的 神人 故事沒有完結 , 因為 耶和華 曾 嚴令他不能在伯特利吃飯喝水 (13:9), 但 一個在伯特利的老先知 卻 騙 他 到 去他 家中吃飯喝水 , 結果在回家的路上 , 神人 遇上獅子將他咬死 , 神人被先知欺騙而死 , 究竟要說明甚麼信息 ? A. 神人被老先知欺騙 , 11-18 B. 神人回家時被咬死 , 19-32 C. 耶波羅安仍然行惡 , 33-34 
「我也是先知，和你一樣。有天使奉耶和華的命對我說：『你去把他帶回你的家，叫他吃飯喝水。』」 (18), 原來直斥耶羅波安之非只是這故事的序幕 , 當這神人聽到那個老先知對他說出這樣的話時 , 他就信以為真 , 以為神改變了先前的嚴令 , 於是跟隨老先知往他他的家去。 
「耶和華如此說：你既違背耶和華的話，不遵守耶和華你神的命令 … 」 (21-22), 情況很可能是當那個神人在老先知家還沒有開始吃飯 ( 或才開始吃飯而仍沒有吃完時 ), 老先知就對他說出這樣的話 , 這個神人顯然沒有因聽到這些話而覺省沒有謹守聽從神的話 , 而選擇繼續吃下去 , 直至吃喝完了然後才乘老先知的驢離去。在回家的路上 , 可憐這個曾經怒斥耶羅波安的先知竟被獅子咬死 , 竟然因為違背耶和華的話，而客死異鄉 , 他的屍身不得入他列祖的墳墓 。 
「 這事以後，耶羅波安仍不離開他的惡道，將凡民立為邱壇的祭司 … 」 (33-34) 。 金牛犢的敬拜使尼八的兒子耶羅波安為首的北國在地上除滅是這個故事序幕的宣告 , [1] 在回家的路上 , 這個猶大的先知死了 , 他的死要告訴讀者甚麼信息 ? 
這個 故事 說明即使曾經被神使用的人 , 當他違背神的話 , 一樣要遭受神的懲罰 , 這正是耶羅波安的寫照 ! 神使用耶羅波去懲罰羅波安治下的大衛家 , 但耶羅波安卻在其他許多的事上得罪耶和華。這個故事既藉神人當面的斥責告誡耶羅波安 , 同時也用他的死告誡耶羅波安。 
神揀選的以色列民本來要成為聖潔的國度 , 屬神的子民 , 但他們卻因今生的驕傲 , 肉體的情慾 , 惡者的欺哄 , 一個又一個違背了耶和華的道 , 以致他們都遭受同樣的結局 : 不能與列祖同睡 — 不能領受神給列祖的應許 , [2] 都回不了家 ! 
有人說 , 人生是一個回家路上 (home coming) 的過程 , 神的兒女都要回家 , 回家為了安息在主懷裏 , 為了領受父神的賜福 , 但有回不了家的以色列民 , 他們回不了家 , 非因神的應許不兌現 , 只因這些以色列民不聽從神的話 , 甚至當先知指出他們的罪時 , 仍然頑梗 , 仍不知認罪悔改 , 耶羅波安如此 , 以色列南北國諸王也多是如此 , 祭司如此 , 先知也會如此 ! 我們也會如此嗎 ? 
[1] 這壇必破裂，壇上的灰必傾撒，這是耶和華說的預兆。(13:3) [2] 我必叫你成為大國。我必賜福給你，叫你的名為大；你也要叫別人得福。為你祝福的，我必賜福與他；那咒詛你的，我必咒詛他。地上的萬族都要因你得福。 ( 創 12:2-3) 。
